<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <title>Welcome to Solar Maket!</title>
  <style>
    body{margin:0;padding:0;background:#06080d;font-family:'DM Sans',Arial,sans-serif;color:#e2e8f0}
    .wrap{max-width:560px;margin:40px auto;background:#111827;border:1px solid #1e293b;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden}
    .hero{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#111827 0%,#162032 100%);padding:48px 32px;text-align:center;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.3)}
    .sun{font-size:64px;display:block;margin-bottom:12px}
    .logo{font-size:26px;font-weight:700;color:#f59e0b;letter-spacing:1px}
    .body{padding:36px}
    h2{font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#e2e8f0;margin:0 0 12px}
    p{color:#94a3b8;font-size:15px;line-height:1.65;margin:0 0 16px}
    .features{display:grid;gap:14px;margin:24px 0}
    .feat{background:#162032;border:1px solid #253044;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px}
    .feat-icon{font-size:22px;flex-shrink:0;line-height:1}
    .feat-title{font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#e2e8f0;margin-bottom:3px}
    .feat-desc{font-size:12.5px;color:#94a3b8;line-height:1.5}
    .cta{display:block;background:#f59e0b;color:#000;text-align:center;padding:15px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;text-decoration:none;margin:24px 0}
    .footer{padding:20px 32px;border-top:1px solid #1e293b;text-align:center;font-size:12px;color:#475569}
    .footer a{color:#f59e0b;text-decoration:none}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="hero">
      <span class="sun">☀️</span>
      <div class="logo">Solar Maket Nigeria</div>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <h2>Welcome aboard, {{firstName}}! 🎉</h2>
      <p>You've joined Nigeria's smartest solar marketplace. Whether you're buying, selling, or just exploring — we've got everything you need to go solar.</p>
      <div class="features">
        <div class="feat">
          <div class="feat-icon">🛒</div>
          <div>
            <div class="feat-title">Browse 1,200+ Solar Products</div>
            <div class="feat-desc">Panels, batteries, inverters, controllers — from verified sellers nationwide.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feat">
          <div class="feat-icon">⚡</div>
          <div>
            <div class="feat-title">AI Solar Advisor</div>
            <div class="feat-desc">Tell us your appliances, get 3 complete system designs with ₦ cost estimates.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feat">
          <div class="feat-icon">🏪</div>
          <div>
            <div class="feat-title">Sell Your Products</div>
            <div class="feat-desc">AI-powered spec extraction from product labels. Reach thousands of buyers.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feat">
          <div class="feat-icon">💬</div>
          <div>
            <div class="feat-title">AI + Human Support</div>
            <div class="feat-desc">Expert solar help available instantly — AI first, escalate to a human anytime.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a href="{{frontendUrl}}" class="cta">Start Exploring Solar Maket →</a>
      <p style="font-size:13px">Questions? Just reply to this email or chat with us live on the platform.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      © {{year}} Solar Maket Nigeria Ltd · <a href="{{frontendUrl}}/unsubscribe">Unsubscribe</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
